'''刺刀座'''（{{Lang-en|Bayonet lug}}）是在大多數軍事[[鳥銃|鳥銃]]、[[步枪|步枪]]和[[散彈槍|散彈槍]]，以及一部份民用[[長管槍械|長管槍械]]以上的標準配置。它用於連接{{Link-en|刺型刺刀|Spike bayonet|刺型}}或{{Link-en|匕首型刺刀|Knife bayonet|匕首}}型狀的[[刺刀|刺刀]]。

== 概述 ==
刺刀座是一款金屬支架，用以將刺刀鎖定在武器以上或為刺刀提供支撐的基座，因此當刺刀穿刺對象時，刺刀不會移動或向後滑動。不到400年前，尚未有刺刀座或它們的前身使得它們滑過槍管。

在刺刀座得以發明之前，使用的是填塞型刺刀，即是把緊身的刀柄塞在[[槍口|鳥銃口]]的末端；這實際上導致鳥銃幾乎物無所用，而且必然地妨礙鳥銃的擊發。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Norris|first=John|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jK_kCwAAQBAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PT22&dq=%22Plug+bayonets%22&hl=en|title=Fix Bayonets!|date=2016-01-03|publisher=Pen and Sword|isbn=978-1-4738-8378-9|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427171629/https://books.google.com/books?id=jK_kCwAAQBAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PT22&dq=%22Plug+bayonets%22&hl=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=|first=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZCmUeb52l3MC&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA164&dq=%22Plug+bayonets%22&hl=en|title=Military History: The Definitive Visual Guide to the Objects of Warfare|date=2012-10-01|publisher=DK Publishing|year=|isbn=978-1-4654-1158-7|editor-last=Jones|editor-first=Gareth|location=|pages=|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427173638/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZCmUeb52l3MC&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA164&dq=%22Plug+bayonets%22&hl=en}}</ref>但是到了17世紀末期，這類刺刀被完全淘汰，隨後被插座式刺刀取代；它將刀身偏向側面，或是剛好在上方或下方突出，以偏離槍口。然後插座式刺刀被按扣和刺刀座所取代。<ref>{{Cite book|last=|first=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JHNnAAAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&q=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|title=Bulletin|date=|publisher=Military Historical Society (Great Britain)|year=1973|isbn=|volume=Vol 24|location=University of Michigan|pages=|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021015404/https://books.google.com/books?id=JHNnAAAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&q=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>刺刀座通常位於鳥銃、步槍或其他長槍[[槍管|槍管]]的[[槍口|槍口]]末端附近<ref>{{Cite book|last=Office|first=United States Patent and Trademark|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SQXPAAAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|title=Official Gazette of the United States Patent and Trademark Office: Patents|date=1987|publisher=U.S. Department of Commerce, Patent and Trademark Office|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121083357/https://books.google.com/books?id=SQXPAAAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。偶爾，刺刀座如果兼用作準星座，會將其設在槍管的頂部；但更常見的是將其安裝在槍管的側邊或底部。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Chapel|first=Charles Edward|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AcXDAgAAQBAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PT181&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|title=Guns of the Old West: An Illustrated Guide|date=2012-05-24|publisher=Courier Corporation|isbn=978-0-486-16306-2|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427172037/https://books.google.com/books?id=AcXDAgAAQBAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PT181&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Moller|first=George D.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I3kq9F06yw0C&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA88&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|title=American Military Shoulder Arms, Volume I: Colonial and Revolutionary War Arms|date=2011-11-15|publisher=UNM Press|isbn=978-0-8263-4996-5|language=en|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021015406/https://books.google.com/books?id=I3kq9F06yw0C&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA88&dq=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Pauly|first=Roger|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HMMqAQAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&q=%22Bayonet+lug%22&hl=en|title=Firearms: The Life Story of a Technology|date=2008-04-28|publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press|year=|isbn=978-0-8018-8836-6|location=Northwestern University|pages=|language=en}}</ref>

== 款式 ==
與值得收藏的軍用槍械不同，基於其軍用版本的民用槍械通常在各國、各州受到法律問題所約束。眾多生產商甚至都不用費心於製造刺刀座。根據現已過期的1994年{{Link-en|聯邦突擊武器禁制法案|Federal Assault Weapons Ban}}（簡稱：AWB）規定，新槍械不能具有刺刀座。而在該法律的背景以下，[[美国全国步枪协会|美国全国步枪协会]]卻將{{Link-en|伸縮式槍托|Telescoping stock}}視為“化妝品般的特性”。<ref name="NRA040913">{{cite web |author=<!--no byline--> |date=2004年9月13日 |title=Finally, the End of a Sad Era--Clinton Gun Ban Stricken from Books! |url=http://www.nraila.org/legislation/federal-legislation/2004/finally,-the-end-of-a-sad-era-clinton.aspx |publisher=美國全國步槍協會，立法行動研究所（National Rifle Association, Institute for Legislative Action） |location=弗吉尼亞州費爾法克斯（Fairfax, Virginia） |quote=不過，奉公守法的公民將可再度免費購買半自動槍械，無論其外觀特徵如何，用於標靶射擊、射擊競賽、狩獵、收藏，和最重要的是自衛用途。（Law-abiding citizens, however, will once again be free to purchase semi-automatic firearms, regardless of their cosmetic features, for target shooting, shooting competitions, hunting, collecting, and most importantly, self-defense.） |accessdate=2020年10月13日 |archive-date=2014年9月15日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915175929/http://www.nraila.org/legislation/federal-legislation/2004/finally,-the-end-of-a-sad-era-clinton.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>舉例來說，目前出售的大多數{{Link-en|AR-15樣式步槍|AR-15 style rifle|AR}}上機匣都無刺刀座，因為它們通常配備了自由浮動式四面導軌配置，附有隱藏的導氣箍，所以無法安裝刺刀。

